title: Bullish Two Hundred Day Moving Average Cross - GUNR - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Wednesday, shares of the GUNR ETF (Symbol: GUNR) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $31.75, changing hands as high as $31.88 per share. GUNR shares are currently trading up about 0.8% on the day.
